OL,3,CUS and Israel accused of overselling
OL,4,Cmilitary success in Iran
OL,6,FKey allies of the US and Israel have
OL,7,Fcast doubt on American and Israeli
OL,8,Fclaims about the extent of military
OL,9,Fsuccess over Iran and the length of
OL,10,Fthis war.
OL,12,FThose claims come as President Trump
OL,13,Fextends a deadline to hit Iranian
OL,14,Fpower sites if the Strait of Hormuz is
OL,15,Fnot fully reopened.
OL,17,FThe president said on Truth Social
OL,18,Fthat he would hold off until the end
OL,19,Fof the week, claiming success in talks
OL,20,Fwith Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
