OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774285870
OL,3,CUS and Israel accused of overselling
OL,4,Cmilitary success in Iran
OL,6,FHowever, Iran has denied any direct
OL,7,Fcontact and accused the president of
OL,8,Fbacking down in fear of Iranian
OL,9,Freprisals across the Gulf.
OL,11,FFour intelligence sources we have
OL,12,Fspoken with have questioned claims
OL,13,Fmade by President Trump and Prime
OL,14,FMinister Netanyahu as to the impact of
OL,15,Fthe war on Iran's military capability.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
