CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774285870
OL,3,CUS and Israel accused of overselling
OL,4,Cmilitary success in Iran
OL,6,FITV News has spoken to intelligence
OL,7,Fsources in a number of allied nations
OL,8,Fin the West and the Middle East, all
OL,9,Fof whom shared concerns that the Trump
OL,10,Fadministration is overselling Iranian
OL,11,Fmilitary losses and underselling the
OL,12,Fpossible length of the war.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
