OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1774285870
OL,3,CUS and Israel accused of overselling
OL,4,Cmilitary success in Iran
OL,6,FA western intelligence source said
OL,7,Fthat while Iran's missile capabilities
OL,8,Fare degraded, "we take all US and
OL,9,FIsraeli reports with caution, our
OL,10,Festimation is that Iran could continue
OL,11,Fin the same rhythm for six months with
OL,12,Ftens of thousands of drones still
OL,13,Funtouched and military production not
OL,14,Feliminated."
OL,16,FOur source told us that while missile-
OL,17,Flaunching capabilities have been
OL,18,Fseverely hit, Iran is estimated to
OL,19,Fhave 50% of its missile capabilities
OL,20,Fintact.
OL,26,@pD@OOUvD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
