OL,3,CUS and Israel accused of overselling
OL,4,Cmilitary success in Iran
OL,6,FOur four sources contradict claims
OL,7,Fmade by Prime Minister Netanyahu on
OL,8,FFriday, "that Iran today has no
OL,9,Fpossibility to enrich uranium and no
OL,10,Fpossibility to produce ballistic
OL,11,Fmissiles."
OL,13,FThe prime minister echoed comments
OL,14,Ffrom US Secretary of War, Pete
OL,15,FHegseth, on March 13 when he claimed:
OL,16,F"As of two days ago, Iran's entire
OL,17,Fballistic missile production capacity
OL,18,F` every company that builds every
OL,19,Fcomponent of those missiles`has been
OL,20,Ffunctionally defeated, destroyed."
OL,26,@pD@IOUsD@JO]xD@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
