OL,3,CUS and Israel accused of overselling
OL,4,Cmilitary success in Iran
OL,6,FA senior regional intelligence source,
OL,7,Fmeanwhile, said the Iranian military
OL,8,Fcapabilities and its proxies'
OL,9,Fcapabilities were miscalculated by the
OL,10,FUS and Israel, and the figures
OL,11,Fprovided by them cannot be trusted.
OL,13,FWhy does this matter? Because the
OL,14,Fworld could be facing a much longer
OL,15,Fwar than America is willing to
OL,16,Facknowledge, with the human and
OL,17,Feconomic fallout which comes with that.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
