OL,3,CUS and Israel accused of overselling
OL,4,Cmilitary success in Iran
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FI understand that within the
OL,12,Fintelligence community in the UK and
OL,13,Fother countries, worry about the
OL,14,Fveracity of US assessments "has been
OL,15,Fthe case for some time," however, the
OL,16,Fgravity of the current situation has
OL,17,Felevated those concerns.
