OL,3,CUS and Israel accused of overselling
OL,4,Cmilitary success in Iran
OL,6,FAt the same time, American
OL,7,Fintelligence has been degraded,
OL,8,Fleaving greater reliance on Israeli
OL,9,Fassessments and a vulnerability to
OL,10,Ftheir narrative.
OL,12,FFurthermore, two sources told me that
OL,13,Fan unwillingness to deliver a truthful
OL,14,Fassessment to President Trump is
OL,15,Fhaving a knock-on effect down the
OL,16,Fchain of command.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
